channel.title: Delphi: RS Private Server Console, made by me
channel.description:
[center][b][size=15pt]RuneScape Private Server console[/size][/b][/center] [center]~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~[/center]
[b]Description[/b] [i]I have just released my RuneScape Private Server console. Stuck on finding your compiler, runner or compile and runner? Than download this! A little application that allows you to run or compile your server fast. Please don't flame about this![/i]
[b]Usage[/b] [i][b]You need to change the names of these batch files from your server:[/b] the compiler: compile.bat the runner: runserver.bat the compile and runner: compile_and_run.bat
extract this app into your main server source map, and run it.[/i]
[b]Download[/b] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?action=dlattach;topic=94977.0;attach=6453][i][img]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/Themes/default/images/icons/clip.gif[/img] Download from MoparScape[/i][/url]
[b]Screenshot[/b] [i]If many people request this, i want to upload one.[/i]
[b]Credits[/b] [i][b]Jakkie123[/b] 95%: Builded the program [b]Freddy1990[/b] 5%: said how to make an URL in Delphi (thanks Freddy)[/i]
[center]~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~[/center]
[b]Note: If this is the wrong section: sorry, and move this.
No viruses, I SWEAR![/b]
[center]~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~[/center]
[size=8pt][i]Sorry for my not-so-good English language... [b]and if you need help, post your question! also post some [u]FEEDBACK[/u] please?[/b][/i][/size]
